      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 17:38:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>当美国浮动贸易调查时，请寻求关键矿物的清晰度</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/clarity-sought-on-critical-minerals-as-us-floats-trade-probe</link>
      <description><![CDATA[白宫正在浮出水面，即可能对关键矿物进口的关税进行关税调查，从而在唐纳德·特朗普总统优先考虑的关键市场上进一步混淆。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/clarity-sought-on-critical-minerals-as-us-floats-trade-probe</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 17:06:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普的最低关税10％使寻求交易的国家更加困难</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/nations-seeking-to-cut-trade-deals-with-trump-face-10-hurdle</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）的广泛关税宣布使外国领导人竞选与总统的交易，以降低对美国出口的关税。谈判窗口可能比他们想象的要小。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/nations-seeking-to-cut-trade-deals-with-trump-face-10-hurdle</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 17:00:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>敦促司法部不解散其重组的税款</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/doj-is-urged-not-to-dissolve-its-tax-division-in-restructuring</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国前税务官员敦促美国司法部不要在机构范围内的重组中拆除其税收司，并警告说，这样的举动将妨碍执法。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/doj-is-urged-not-to-dissolve-its-tax-division-in-restructuring</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 16:59:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法国的马克龙敦促欧盟公司暂停美国投资</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/france-s-macron-urges-companies-to-pause-us-investments</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国总统伊曼纽尔·马克龙（Emmanuel Macron）敦促公司在唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统宣布对欧洲联盟和其他地区的关税之后暂停在美国的投资。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/france-s-macron-urges-companies-to-pause-us-investments</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 14:40:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德国和法国推动更积极的关税回应</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/germany-and-france-push-for-a-more-aggressive-tariff-response</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国和德国正在推动对美国总统唐纳德·特朗普的关税措施做出更强有力的反应，并提倡有力的报复，这可以加强欧盟的谈判立场。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/germany-and-france-push-for-a-more-aggressive-tariff-response</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 10:52:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
